flowchart LR
  Aim[GoalOSCommit / Aim] --> Act[RunCommitment / Act]
  Act --> Proof[ProofRoot + ProofBundle]
  Proof --> Replay[Replay Registry]
  Replay --> Eval[Eval + Commit-Reveal Validation]
  Eval --> Select[Selection Gate]
  Select --> Rollout[Rollout / Rollback]
  Rollout --> Docket[Evidence Docket]
  Docket --> Chronicle[Chronicle]
  Chronicle --> Conform[AEP Conformance]
  Conform --> Reputation[Credentials + Reputation + alpha-WU]
